description: Tarsin Mobile, Inc. engages in the development, production, distribution, finance, and marketing of feature films and television programming. The company, through its subsidiary, Empire Sports Group, Inc., develops, acquires, produces, markets, and distributes sports related entertainment properties. The company was formerly known as Empire Film Group, Inc. and changed its name to Tarsin Mobile, Inc. in June 2015. Tarsin Mobile, Inc. is based in Westlake Village, California.
